Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,欢迎加入OCR小组 qq群906722936 字幕优先发布于群内
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:23.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,前情提要\N特伦查德大人 全额付款\N{\rYUANWEN}Lord Trenchard. Payment in full.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:26.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,啊 他家夫人十分美丽\N{\rYUANWEN}Ah. He of the beautiful wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:28.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,埃勒比医生\N{\rYUANWEN}Dr. Ellerby.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:30.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,艺术展览的邀请函\N{\rYUANWEN}An invitation to an art exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:32.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这位医生倒是很执着\N{\rYUANWEN}He's persistent, the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:34.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是在表示友好罢了\N{\rYUANWEN}He's being friendly, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.14,0:00:39.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嘘 跟我来\N{\rYUANWEN}Shh. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:41.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道那家炼钢厂吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You know about the steel foundry?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:43.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我在考虑对它投资\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm thinking of investing in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:45.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一大笔钱 老爷\N{\rYUANWEN}A lot of money, Your Lordship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:47.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看来您满意了 夫人\N{\rYUANWEN}You're satisfied then, madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:49.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我希望名下的所有投资都一帆风顺\N{\rYUANWEN}I wish all my investments ran as smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:51.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希望不久再合作新项目\N{\rYUANWEN}We must plan another venture together soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:56.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:00:59.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你怎么了  -我想起了我的父亲\N{\rYUANWEN}·What is it? - I was thinking about my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:02.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他一定会为你骄傲的\N{\rYUANWEN}He'd be proud of you, surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:04.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我个人认为 逃避不良情绪\N{\rYUANWEN}Personally, I think it's in our natures
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.01,0:01:05.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是人的天性\N{\rYUANWEN}to run away from difficult feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:06.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但只要鼓起勇气面对\N{\rYUANWEN}But if we have the courage to confront them,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:09.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就能放下很多痛苦\N{\rYUANWEN}we can let go of a great deal of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.14,0:01:11.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我哥最近怎么样\N{\rYUANWEN}How is my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.18,0:01:15.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他对他父亲有些心结 并深受其困\N{\rYUANWEN}He is very much troubled by thoughts of his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:18.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你要是能跟弗雷德里克谈谈 会大有裨益\N{\rYUANWEN}It might help Frederick if you would speak to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你想把她变成你的朋友\N{\rYUANWEN}You thought you would befriend her
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.57,0:01:24.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,然后在她耳边说我坏话\N{\rYUANWEN}and whisper poison in her ears about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.28,0:01:26.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,- 不 我没有  -请你离开我家\N{\rYUANWEN}- No, I didn't. - Leave my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:30.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你背着我去见他了\N{\rYUANWEN}You went behind my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.91,0:01:34.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你为什么要这么做  -我不知情啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Why would you do that? - I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:03:01.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你第一次见他是什么时候\N{\rYUANWEN}When did you first meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:02.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一个多星期前\N{\rYUANWEN}A little over a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:04.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在哪儿见的\N{\rYUANWEN}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:08.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我说过了 我去了牧师住宅\N{\rYUANWEN}I told you. I went to the vicarage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:09.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就一次\N{\rYUANWEN}Once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:12.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是了解我的\N{\rYUANWEN}You know me well enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:14.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道我心里只有你\N{\rYUANWEN}You know I think only of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:16.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我以为能帮你解开心结\N{\rYUANWEN}I thought it might help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:19.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你的内心 藏了太多的痛苦\N{\rYUANWEN}You have so much pain locked in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:21.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你就是这么看我的 一个需要救助的\N{\rYUANWEN}That's how you see me? As some injured creature
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:23.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-受伤动物  -不\N{\rYUANWEN}who must be helped? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:24.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-这是他暗示你的吧  -不\N{\rYUANWEN}- Is that what he implied? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:25.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他都说我什么了\N{\rYUANWEN}What did he say about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:27.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他说你跟你父亲有过节\N{\rYUANWEN}That there was a rift with your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:28.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这不是你造成的\N{\rYUANWEN}which was not of your making.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:31.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-真有雅量啊  -他说他很想你\N{\rYUANWEN}·How magnanimous. - He said he misses you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:33.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他渴望与你和解\N{\rYUANWEN}that he longs to be reconciled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:36.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他表现得真诚 弗雷德里克\N{\rYUANWEN}He seemed genuine, Frederick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:38.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,说实话 我依然相信 只要你们能坐下来聊聊\N{\rYUANWEN}Honestly, I still believe that if you could only talk together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:40.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你根本不了解他\N{\rYUANWEN}You don't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:52.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道他有个弟弟吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Did you know he had a brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:54.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然知道\N{\rYUANWEN}Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:55.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,两个男生在格兰维尔长大时\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Enright and I were at Glanville
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:57.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就是恩莱特先生和我在伺候了\N{\rYUANWEN}when the two boys were growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:58.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以是发生了什么\N{\rYUANWEN}So, what went on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,两人肯定是有天大的矛盾\N{\rYUANWEN}It must've been an almighty falling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:01.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很多兄弟都有矛盾\N{\rYUANWEN}Lots of brothers fall out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:05.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对 可是\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我也总跟我哥闹矛盾\N{\rYUANWEN}I fell out of my lot all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:08.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是说 我们会吵架\N{\rYUANWEN}I mean, we had fights,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:10.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也会打架 一连打上好几小时\N{\rYUANWEN}punch- ups that went on for hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:12.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-是吗  -当然\N{\rYUANWEN}Did you? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:13.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但等你俩坐在桌前\N{\rYUANWEN}But then you sit down at the table,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:15.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,妈妈端上来一碗热乎乎的炖菜时\N{\rYUANWEN}and your ma gives you a bowl of stew
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:17.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,矛盾就到此结束\N{\rYUANWEN}·and that's the end of it. -
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们要上去了\N{\rYUANWEN}They're going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:29.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这件事今后谁也不许再提 无论是在府内还是府外\N{\rYUANWEN}None of this is to be discussed outside this house or in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希望大家都能理解\N{\rYUANWEN}I hope that's understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,明白\N{\rYUANWEN}It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:36.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,都解散吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:38.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-晚安 恩薰特先生  -晚安\N{\rYUANWEN}·Good night then, Mr. Enright. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:56.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以 这俩兄弟还闹着矛盾呢\N{\rYUANWEN}So, things are still bad between the brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:58.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,似乎是这样\N{\rYUANWEN}Seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:04:59.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他俩的事我从没弄明白过\N{\rYUANWEN}I never really understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他俩的事我从没弄明白过\N{\rYUANWEN}I never really understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:04.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是嫉妒吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is it jealousy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:06.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-是竞争吗  -我知道的不比你多\N{\rYUANWEN}Rivalry? - I know no more than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:09.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我天天困在厨房里 能知道什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What do I see stuck in the kitchen all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:14.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你怎么这么难受 人都在抖\N{\rYUANWEN}Why does it bother you so much? You're shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:16.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我辜负了他\N{\rYUANWEN}I failed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:19.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我应该想法子提醒他的 玛德琳\N{\rYUANWEN}I should have found a way to warn him, Madeleine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:22.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我应该想法子提醒他的 玛德琳\N{\rYUANWEN}I should have found a way to warn him, Madeleine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:25.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是个成年人了 也该会自己处理麻烦了\N{\rYUANWEN}He's a grown man. Let him deal with his own mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:33.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,用的是我奶奶的食谱\N{\rYUANWEN}From my grandmama's recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:36.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然 我很少冒险下厨\N{\rYUANWEN}I rarely venture into the kitchen, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:37.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但如果您吃起来不错\N{\rYUANWEN}but if it meets with your approval,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:40.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我打算做五个 拿到蛋糕摊上去卖\N{\rYUANWEN}I shall be supplying five for the cake stall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:45.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是我吃过的最好吃的水果蛋糕\N{\rYUANWEN}That is the finest fruit cake I have ever tasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:47.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我吃过的蛋糕也不少\N{\rYUANWEN}And I have tasted a good many.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:50.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那好 就这么定了\N{\rYUANWEN}Good. That's decided then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:52.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我就甩开膀子干了\N{\rYUANWEN}I shall set my shoulder to the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:54.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:59.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,听说您见过我妹妹了\N{\rYUANWEN}I hear you met my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:04.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对的 相见甚欢\N{\rYUANWEN}I did. It was a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:08.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然 她很有魅力\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, yes, she's all charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,苛以及时到\N{\rYUANWEN}...there in good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:18.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们时间算得不错 夫人\N{\rYUANWEN}I...I think we timed that well, Your Ladyship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:20.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,天再过半个小时会很热\N{\rYUANWEN}It'll be so hot in half an hour
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:23.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,散步就不会很适宜了\N{\rYUANWEN}that there'd be no pleasure in a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:35.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我能做些什么吗\N{\rYUANWEN}How can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:41.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,给夫人的信\N{\rYUANWEN}Your Ladyship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:43.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我让他们您倒点咖啡来吧 夫人\N{\rYUANWEN}Shall I ask them to bring you some coffee, Your Ladyship?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:46.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好的 拜托\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:49.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,戴维森\N{\rYUANWEN}Davison?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:00.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-牧师  -请原谅\N{\rYUANWEN}Reverend. - Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:03.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只求您给我五分钟\N{\rYUANWEN}Five minutes of your time is all I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:14.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想这是我们最后一次见面了\N{\rYUANWEN}I think this will be the last time we ever meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:17.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,恐怕你说的对\N{\rYUANWEN}I fear that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:20.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想对你说两件事\N{\rYUANWEN}I want to say two things to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:24.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很抱歉昨天直接登门贵府\N{\rYUANWEN}I am so sorry I came to the house yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:25.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不该那么做的\N{\rYUANWEN}I should never have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:28.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是我的错 我给了你希望\N{\rYUANWEN}It was my fault. I gave you hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我 我一想到自己让你跟\N{\rYUANWEN}I...I can't live with the thought
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:33.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,弗雷德里克起了隔阂 就很过意不去\N{\rYUANWEN}that I've caused difficulty between you and Frederick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:36.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,特伦查德夫人 请别他的表现\N{\rYUANWEN}Lady Trenchard, please don't think badly of him
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:38.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,和这些事影响他在你心中的看法\N{\rYUANWEN}for the way he behaved yesterday or for any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:41.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这不能怪他\N{\rYUANWEN}He's not to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:44.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请您保证会永远记得这一点\N{\rYUANWEN}Please tell me you will always remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:47.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我真希望能多了解一些\N{\rYUANWEN}I wish I understood more about what happened with your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:49.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们父子之间的事\N{\rYUANWEN}and with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:54.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他的态度非常 强硬\N{\rYUANWEN}His attitude is so...entrenched.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:56.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们是发生了什么特别的事吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Was there one particular event?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:57.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是大吵了一架吗\N{\rYUANWEN}An argument?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:02.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他提到 你父亲临终时\N{\rYUANWEN}He mentioned that when your father was dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:05.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只想让你陪在床边\N{\rYUANWEN}he wanted only you at his bedside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:06.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是真的吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:08.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这\N{\rYUANWEN}It.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:10.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是我父亲的决定\N{\rYUANWEN}It was my father's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:12.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不能违背他的意愿\N{\rYUANWEN}And I couldn't go against his wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:18.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那你母亲呢 她就没劝劝他吗\N{\rYUANWEN}And what of your mother? Couldn't she have persuaded him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:22.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,家母是一位坚强美丽的女人\N{\rYUANWEN}Our mother was a strong and beautiful woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:24.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但她同时也希望别人\N{\rYUANWEN}but she expected the same strength
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:27.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,像她一样坚强\N{\rYUANWEN}in everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:29.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那在她去世时\N{\rYUANWEN}And when she died,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,应该是想见到弗雷迪里克的吧\N{\rYUANWEN}please tell me she wanted Frederick there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:32.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她想见\N{\rYUANWEN}She did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:34.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,非常想见他\N{\rYUANWEN}Very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:36.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她专门提出见他\N{\rYUANWEN}She asked for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:39.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们是那个时候闹了矛盾吗\N{\rYUANWEN}And did anything happen between you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:41.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那是你们最后一次见面吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Was that the last time you saw one another?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:44.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他没能过来\N{\rYUANWEN}He wasn't able to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:47.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但他来参加了葬礼 可我们没有说话\N{\rYUANWEN}But he came to the funeral, though we didn't speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:51.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她临终时\N{\rYUANWEN}He didn't go to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:53.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他没去见她\N{\rYUANWEN}when she was dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:54.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,为什么呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:57.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得\N{\rYUANWEN}I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:59.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许是因为恐惧\N{\rYUANWEN}perhaps it was the fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:01.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许会激起他对家父去世的回忆\N{\rYUANWEN}the memory of our father's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:06.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许他不来更好\N{\rYUANWEN}Perhaps it was better that he didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:09.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你怎么会这么说呢\N{\rYUANWEN}How can you say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:14.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没有什么能阻止我见父亲最后一面\N{\rYUANWEN}Nothing would have kept me from my father's deathbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他受伤极深\N{\rYUANWEN}The wounds are deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:17.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:20.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是经年累月的\N{\rYUANWEN}It was years...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:24.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,任何人都难以承受这种伤害\N{\rYUANWEN}It would be too much for any soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:27.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我总觉得\N{\rYUANWEN}I can't help feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:29.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你还有事瞒着我\N{\rYUANWEN}that there's something you're not telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:32.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很抱歉这么说 但有没有什么信息\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm sorry, but if there's anything, anything at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:35.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,能帮我更好地了解他 什么信息都行\N{\rYUANWEN}which might help me to understand him better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只能说到这里了\N{\rYUANWEN}There is no more to be said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:42.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,失去他我也很悲伤\N{\rYUANWEN}My own sadness at the loss of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是我必须承受的\N{\rYUANWEN}I must bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:47.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我也会承受\N{\rYUANWEN}I will bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:50.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但 但请向我保证 他会永远\N{\rYUANWEN}But...But I have to know that he will always,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:51.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,永远拥有你的爱和支持\N{\rYUANWEN}always have your love and support.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:57.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:06.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这不是他的错\N{\rYUANWEN}He was not to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:16.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以 我想问问各位女士\N{\rYUANWEN}So, I'm asking the ladies if they have experience
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:19.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有没有照顾大象的经验\N{\rYUANWEN}in looking after the elephants. -
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:22.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那只白象 亲爱的海蒂\N{\rYUANWEN}The white elephant, Hetty dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:24.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,白象摊位\N{\rYUANWEN}White Elephant Stall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:27.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这个职位蛮特别的\N{\rYUANWEN}It's a very different proposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:28.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们又不招驯象员\N{\rYUANWEN}We are not recruiting mahouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:53.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看到了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You see there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:54.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们重新加入了碳和锰\N{\rYUANWEN}They're reintroducing carbon and manganese.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:57.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,份量不多不少\N{\rYUANWEN}Exact amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:01.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真厉害 非常厉害\N{\rYUANWEN}Damned impressive! Damned impressivel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:03.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就像地狱之口\N{\rYUANWEN}Like the mouth of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:04.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你果然是懂行的  -那当然\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm glad you're able to see it. - I'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:06.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你邀请我过来\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you for inviting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:09.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,想想看 这个工厂会全年无休地开工\N{\rYUANWEN}To think that is going all day, every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:12.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-日夜不停  -太棒了\N{\rYUANWEN}And through the night. - It's astonishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:15.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,敬你一杯 这个聪明鬼\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, to you, my clever friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:19.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,以及他不断扩张的王国 伦敦东区异类\N{\rYUANWEN}and his expanding kingdom, the strange land of East End.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:24.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,难怪连侯爵夫人都被你打动了\N{\rYUANWEN}No wonder the Marquise is so impressed by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:27.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她总是对你赞不绝口\N{\rYUANWEN}Never tires of singing your praises.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:30.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道她有个新项目 还想邀我一起干吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You know she's trying to enlist me into this new scheme of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:33.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她也邀请你了吧 一定请了\N{\rYUANWEN}Did you put her up to it? I suspect you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:35.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,啊是的\N{\rYUANWEN}Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:36.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-哪一个  -银矿那个\N{\rYUANWEN}Which one? - The silver mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:38.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在墨西哥\N{\rYUANWEN}Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:40.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,估计我在地图上都找不到\N{\rYUANWEN}Doubt I could place it on a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:44.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但她对这个项目似乎很有信心 对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}She seems utterly confident in the venture, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:45.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你怎么看\N{\rYUANWEN}What do you think of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:47.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,显然 我还需要更多信息\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, I need more information, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:48.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,太对了\N{\rYUANWEN}Quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:51.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,涉及到数字的地方 我就不知道了\N{\rYUANWEN}The figures involved. I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:53.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我告诉她 做生意我不太在行\N{\rYUANWEN}I told her business isn't my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:54.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:56.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但作为一个小投资来说 还挺令人兴奋的\N{\rYUANWEN}For a first little foray, it seems rather thrilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:12:02.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去异国土地上淘金\N{\rYUANWEN}"Untold riches in an exotic land. "
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:05.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她什么时候跟你提的 我好奇问一下\N{\rYUANWEN}When did she mention it to you? Out of interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:06.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大约一周前\N{\rYUANWEN}About a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,怎么 我错过截止日期了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't tell me I've missed the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:11.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嗯 没 没有\N{\rYUANWEN}Uh...no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:13.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,至少我不这么认为\N{\rYUANWEN}At least I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:15.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我跟着你投就对了\N{\rYUANWEN}I shall be led by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,今后就是合作伙伴了哈\N{\rYUANWEN}Rather jolly to be partners, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:24.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得过几天\N{\rYUANWEN}I thought we might go out together
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.02,0:12:25.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,咱俩可以出门走走\N{\rYUANWEN}sometime in the next few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:28.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我之前跟你说过的画展\N{\rYUANWEN}The exhibition of paintings I mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:30.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还记得吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:32.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就是明天\N{\rYUANWEN}It's tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:33.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,咱俩一起去好不好\N{\rYUANWEN}I thought we might attend together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:34.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,恐怕我抽不出时间\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm afraid I can't spare the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:38.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但你要是想去就去吧\N{\rYUANWEN}but you should go if you'd like to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:40.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一个人去吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:41.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不过我有点弄不懂\N{\rYUANWEN}Although I must say I'm surprised,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:45.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,邀请函不是埃勒比医生寄来的吗\N{\rYUANWEN}was the invitation not from Dr. Ellerby?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:49.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对但据我所知 展出的作品不是他的\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, but the works are not his, from what I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:52.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他只想引起我们的注意\N{\rYUANWEN}He was simply bringing it to our attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:53.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许罗切斯特一家也会去\N{\rYUANWEN}I thought the Rochesters might attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,估计不会\N{\rYUANWEN}- - I doubt they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:57.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那咱们千点别的吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, let's do something else then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:12:58.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得如果有机会\N{\rYUANWEN}It might be good for us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:00.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我们可以  -克拉拉\N{\rYUANWEN}to have the opportunity to- - - Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:04.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我已经认真想过了 我希望\N{\rYUANWEN}I have thought on this, and it is my wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:07.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你我努力忘掉昨天的不愉快\N{\rYUANWEN}that we endeavor to forget the events of yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:08.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,弗雷德里克\N{\rYUANWEN}Frederick- -
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:10.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,虽然我费了很大地劲儿\N{\rYUANWEN}I accept, albeit with some difficulty,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:13.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,才理解你想办好事的初衷\N{\rYUANWEN}that you thought your actions might be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:15.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我理解这一点\N{\rYUANWEN}I accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:20.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但坦白讲 我不想每晚坐在餐桌旁\N{\rYUANWEN}But frankly, I cannot sit at dinner every night,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:23.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,都等着我妻子又一次提出那个\N{\rYUANWEN}wondering when my wife will insist on raising matters
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:27.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只会给我带来不悦的问题\N{\rYUANWEN}that can only be the cause of the deepest discomfort to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:29.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我希望你能理解\N{\rYUANWEN}I hope you are able to understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:34.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我能理解 是的\N{\rYUANWEN}I am able to understand it. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:40.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我并不是想\N{\rYUANWEN}I didn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.81,0:13:44.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,拜托 求你了 今后别再提了\N{\rYUANWEN}Please...Please, can we leave it at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我只是得了些闲空\N{\rYUANWEN}Sorry. I had a few minutes to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:07.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,千万别道歉\N{\rYUANWEN}Please don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:11.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我能问你个问题吗 牧师\N{\rYUANWEN}May I ask you a question, Reverend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:13.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然可以\N{\rYUANWEN}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:16.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你觉得人死后会孤单吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you think the dead feel lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:20.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不觉得\N{\rYUANWEN}No. I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:26.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得天堂是一个充满爱和温暖的地方\N{\rYUANWEN}I think those in heaven feel awash with warmth and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:30.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可那些没进天堂的人呢\N{\rYUANWEN}What if they aren't in heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:31.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们并非是自己犯了错\N{\rYUANWEN}Through no fault of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:34.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,神就是爱\N{\rYUANWEN}God is love
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:36.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,神永远不会拒绝\N{\rYUANWEN}and would never turn someone away
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:37.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一个无辜的人\N{\rYUANWEN}if they were innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:42.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,孤独是种人世的痛苦\N{\rYUANWEN}Loneliness is an earthly affliction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:44.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,即便一屋子坐满了人\N{\rYUANWEN}We can feel lonely
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:46.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们还是会感到痛苦 不是吗\N{\rYUANWEN}even in a room full of people, can't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:51.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是在为某人担心吗 内尔\N{\rYUANWEN}Are you concerned about someone in particular, Nell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:52.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,牧师 你在这里\N{\rYUANWEN}Ah, Reverend, here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:14:56.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,邓恩小姐 你还好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Miss Dunn. How are you getting on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:59.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,能占用你几分钟宝贵的时间吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Might we have a few minutes of your precious time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:00.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我得在明天之前告诉印刷商\N{\rYUANWEN}Only I have to deliver the wording of the handbook
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:02.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,手册的内容\N{\rYUANWEN}to the printers by the end of tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:04.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,筹资目标\N{\rYUANWEN}The fundraising objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:05.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我本该帮你写下来的\N{\rYUANWEN}I was supposed to write them down for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:07.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\rYUANWEN}Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我自己冒昧地列了几项\N{\rYUANWEN}I've taken the liberty of outlining a few myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:11.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,钟表维修需要15英镑\N{\rYUANWEN}Repairs to the clock at 15 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:15.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,墓墙维修 你说过是38英镑\N{\rYUANWEN}Cemetery wall repairs, I think you mentioned at 38 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:17.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,天 您的记忆真是超群\N{\rYUANWEN}My goodness. What a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:20.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对对 咱们现在就敲定\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, yes. Let's look at them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:26.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,内尔 客气提醒下 这些茶杯需要洗了\N{\rYUANWEN}The teacups need washing, Nell, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,下午好\N{\rYUANWEN}Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:38.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-欢迎  -谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}- Welcome. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:42.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是展品目录 供您阅读\N{\rYUANWEN}Our catalogue, if you would care to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:46.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是迪尔登先生 参展人之一\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Dearden. I'm one of the exhibitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我喜欢提前表明身份\N{\rYUANWEN}I always think it best to mention that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:51.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,以免别人说出什么话令我伤心\N{\rYUANWEN}before someone says something which breaks my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,能告诉我您叫什么吗\N{\rYUANWEN}And might I have your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:57.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然 特伦查德夫人\N{\rYUANWEN}Of course. Lady Trenchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:01.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是埃勒比医生邀请我来的\N{\rYUANWEN}I received an invitation from Dr. Ellerby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对对 您能来真是太好了\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes. Yes. How kind of you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:07.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,斯蒂芬 埃勒比医生一定会很开心的\N{\rYUANWEN}Stephen- - Dr. Ellerby- will be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:10.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但恐怕他现在不在\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm afraid he isn't here at present.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:14.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那罗切斯特公爵夫人在里面吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is the Duchess of Rochester here, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:17.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她之前还在\N{\rYUANWEN}She was, earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:19.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要我带你四处看看吗 特伦查德夫人\N{\rYUANWEN}Would you like me to show you around, Lady Trenchard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:23.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我乐意为您效劳  -谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}- I would gladly. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:25.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我自己逛就可以了\N{\rYUANWEN}I shall manage very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:26.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果需要 我随时都在\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm here if you have need of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:47.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我没听说过银矿的事 老爷\N{\rYUANWEN}I've heard nothing at all about a silver mine, Your Lordship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:49.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-不然我一定会记得  -可你还是忘了\N{\rYUANWEN}- I'd remember if I had. - Then you should have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:52.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你炫耀自己人脉时倒是很积极\N{\rYUANWEN}You're quick enough to boast about your contacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:54.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我能问一下背后老板是谁吗\N{\rYUANWEN}May I ask who's behind the scheme?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:56.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要不要我去问问他们\N{\rYUANWEN}Would you like me to make inquiries of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:59.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不用了 我自己会处理\N{\rYUANWEN}No. I shall deal with it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:01.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要是听到什么消息 立刻通知您\N{\rYUANWEN}If I hear anything at all, I shall alert you at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:02.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请您一定放心\N{\rYUANWEN}You may depend on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:38.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,特伦查德夫人正在看的那幅\N{\rYUANWEN}Lady Trenchard is looking at it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:47.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,精巧绝伦 不是吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Extraordinary, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:48.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,埃勒比医生\N{\rYUANWEN}Dr. Ellerby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:50.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,特伦查德女士\N{\rYUANWEN}Lady Trenchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:52.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-戴维森小姐  -先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Miss Davison. - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:54.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大人跟您一起来的吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is His Lordship with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:57.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-遗憾 他没有  -那我就更感激您\N{\rYUANWEN}·Unfortunately not. - Then I'm all the more grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:18:00.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,专程来赴约了\N{\rYUANWEN}that you took the trouble to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:02.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,您以前参观过画廊吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Have you ever visited a gallery before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:04.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有过一次 是和我父亲一起\N{\rYUANWEN}Once, with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:06.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是在皇家艺术学院\N{\rYUANWEN}It was at the Royal Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:09.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但都不如这幅画风格独特\N{\rYUANWEN}There was certainly nothing in this style.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:11.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这话你一定爱听 迪尔登\N{\rYUANWEN}That should be music to your ears, Dearden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:14.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,特伦查德夫人 请允许我介绍\N{\rYUANWEN}Lady Trenchard, allow me to present- -
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:16.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我已有幸认识过了\N{\rYUANWEN}I've already had the pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:18.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是你的作品吗 迪尔登先生\N{\rYUANWEN}This is one of your works, Mr. Dearden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:20.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rYUANWEN}It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:22.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很美\N{\rYUANWEN}It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:25.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,情感丰富 难以言说\N{\rYUANWEN}And emotional, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:28.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,您真是太过奖了\N{\rYUANWEN}I couldn't have hoped for a kinder review.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:30.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你看过罗塞蒂的画作吗  -对\N{\rYUANWEN}·Have you seen the Rossettis? - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我跟他比起来要苍白得多\N{\rYUANWEN}Mine rather pale beside his.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:34.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我持不同看法\N{\rYUANWEN}I can't agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:38.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对 那些作品很吸引人\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, they're arresting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:39.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是我的偶像\N{\rYUANWEN}He's my idol...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:42.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,您大概也看出来了\N{\rYUANWEN}as you can probably tell. -
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:45.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他一会儿会跟莫里斯夫人过来\N{\rYUANWEN}We expect him later, with Mrs. Morris.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:48.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你能留下的话 我可以介绍你们认识\N{\rYUANWEN}If you're able to stay, I will gladly introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:50.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,恐怕我现在得走了\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm afraid I have to leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:53.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -也许下次吧\N{\rYUANWEN}- Thank you. - To the next time, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:57.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那我送您出去\N{\rYUANWEN}Allow me to see you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:19:00.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,您来时我不在 真是抱歉\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm so sorry I wasn't here when you arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:02.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我每周出两次诊\N{\rYUANWEN}I help at a mission twice a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:04.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,今天的病人比平时多\N{\rYUANWEN}And we had more patients than usual today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:09.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你在梅伍德给我的建议\N{\rYUANWEN}The advice you gave me at Maywood,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:11.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,鼓励人们直面恐惧的那一条\N{\rYUANWEN}about encouraging people to confront their fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:13.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:17.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果想帮忙的那个人\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you think it's possible to push too hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:21.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,逼得太紧 会不会把困难复杂化\N{\rYUANWEN}and to compound the difficulty where one was trying to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:23.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我认为任何人\N{\rYUANWEN}I think anyone who's being asked
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:25.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,被问到自己害怕的东西\N{\rYUANWEN}to look at something that frightens them
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:27.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一定会表现出一些阻力\N{\rYUANWEN}is bound to show some resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:29.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,甚至对抗\N{\rYUANWEN}Antagonism, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:32.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我认为 他们内心深处\N{\rYUANWEN}I would say that some part of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:34.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,无论埋得多深\N{\rYUANWEN}no matter how deeply buried,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:35.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,总得自己作出改变\N{\rYUANWEN}would have to want to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:38.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希望我的建议没太冒昧\N{\rYUANWEN}I hope my advice wasn't ill- judged.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:44.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.17,0:19:46.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请别介意我这么说 但你看上去有点伤心\N{\rYUANWEN}You seem a little sad, if you don't mind my saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:53.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我很好\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm perfectly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:55.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,您见过艺术家的工作室吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Have you ever seen inside an artist studio?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:57.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,或者观看过艺术家创作吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Or watched an artist at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:19:59.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我跟迪尔登住在一起\N{\rYUANWEN}I lodge with Dearden,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:03.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他的工作室很有意思 值得一看\N{\rYUANWEN}and his studio is really something to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:04.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果您想来参观\N{\rYUANWEN}If you would ever care to visit. ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:06.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他一定会荣幸至极\N{\rYUANWEN}I know he would be honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:10.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你告诉我\N{\rYUANWEN}I'll bear it in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:28.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对不起 邓恩小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Sorry, Miss Dunn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:30.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你的演奏技艺是哪里学的\N{\rYUANWEN}Where on earth did you learn to play like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:33.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我 嗯\N{\rYUANWEN}I...um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:36.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这不是什么简单小调\N{\rYUANWEN}It's hardly a music hall ditty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.82,0:21:38.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是肖邦吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Chopin, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:43.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只是对曲调过耳不忘\N{\rYUANWEN}I...hear tunes, and they stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:46.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但你是从哪里听到的呢\N{\rYUANWEN}But where could you have heard it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:50.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不记得了\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:53.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:57.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可你却记得所有音符\N{\rYUANWEN}And yet you remember all the notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:21:59.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这天赋真有意思\N{\rYUANWEN}It's quite a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:03.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,家务都做好了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is everything tidied away?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.93,0:22:06.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好的 小姐 我这就去拿工具\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, miss. I'll fetch my things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.53,0:22:13.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们茶都吃完了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}And did you eat all your tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.86,0:22:15.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,吃完了 爸爸\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.82,0:22:17.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好孩子\N{\rYUANWEN}Good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.57,0:22:22.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好了好了 去找保姆吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Now, now, come on, back to Nanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.45,0:22:24.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我跟你一起上楼去看彼得\N{\rYUANWEN}And I shall come upstairs with you and see Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.41,0:22:26.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我能见彼得吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Can I see Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:28.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,彼得病了 对吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Peter is ill, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.12,0:22:30.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他不希望你也生病\N{\rYUANWEN}He doesn't wish for you to get ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.29,0:22:33.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会帮你多亲亲他的\N{\rYUANWEN}I'll give him a kiss from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.67,0:22:38.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你觉得迪尔登先生的画作如何\N{\rYUANWEN}What did you think of Mr. Dearden's paintings?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:41.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我欣赏不来\N{\rYUANWEN}They weren't to my taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.85,0:22:44.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,太华丽了 虽然介绍上写着\N{\rYUANWEN}Too florid. For all the words written in there
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.64,0:22:47.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,自然的真实再现\N{\rYUANWEN}about a"true representation of nature, "
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:51.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,反正看起来跟我熟悉的大自然毫不相干\N{\rYUANWEN}I should say it didn't look anything like the nature I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:55.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得太过夸张浪漫了\N{\rYUANWEN}I should say it was overblown and overly romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.19,0:22:58.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,过于浪漫”难道是坏事吗\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm not sure anything can be"overly romantic. "
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.53,0:23:03.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那是因为你还年轻 夫人\N{\rYUANWEN}That's because you're young, Your Ladyship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.54,0:23:15.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我就先走了 牧师\N{\rYUANWEN}I shall get off now, Reverend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.80,0:23:17.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我留了一些冷盘\N{\rYUANWEN}I've left some cold cuts on the side,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.92,0:23:19.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还留了汤 想喝的话可以喝\N{\rYUANWEN}and there's soup if you'd like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:23.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.43,0:23:24.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你想跟我一起吃吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Would you care to join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.56,0:23:26.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哦 恐怕不行\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, I'm afraid I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:28.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我女儿和她家人还等着我呢\N{\rYUANWEN}My daughter and her family are waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.81,0:23:32.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-好吧  -不过谢谢你了 先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Good. - But thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:34.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那就明早见\N{\rYUANWEN}I shall see you in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.61,0:23:37.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-晚安  -晚安 沃伦夫人\N{\rYUANWEN}·Good night. - Good night, Mrs. Warren.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.09,0:23:57.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他还没回来吗\N{\rYUANWEN}He's not back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.13,0:23:59.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还没有\N{\rYUANWEN}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.55,0:24:01.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他应该在俱乐部吧\N{\rYUANWEN}I believe he is at his club.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.18,0:24:05.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,事业跟婚姻都不顺心\N{\rYUANWEN}Difficult business, marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.60,0:24:08.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,似乎的确如此\N{\rYUANWEN}Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.39,0:24:11.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你自己从没想过结婚吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You never thought of it for yourself, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.94,0:24:13.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我习惯了自由自在\N{\rYUANWEN}I like my own way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.65,0:24:18.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你呢\N{\rYUANWEN}You?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.03,0:24:19.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一样\N{\rYUANWEN}The same.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.54,0:24:29.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢您 老爷\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you, Your Lordship.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.99,0:25:04.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我出去散个步\N{\rYUANWEN}Going for an evening stroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.70,0:25:08.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在我锁门之前回来\N{\rYUANWEN}Back before I lock up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.59,0:25:25.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}- Thank you. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.34,0:28:14.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不是要给我拿煤吗\N{\rYUANWEN}I thought you were fetching me some coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.22,0:28:17.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然 恩莱特太太 别担心\N{\rYUANWEN}Certainly am, Mrs. Enright. Never fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.31,0:28:20.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,麻烦给我一张邮票\N{\rYUANWEN}A stamp for this, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.23,0:28:22.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要寄到哪里\N{\rYUANWEN}Where's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.40,0:28:26.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不识字吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Can't read?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.32,0:28:28.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你自然是不识字的 给我吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Of course you can't. Pass it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.12,0:28:42.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-信是寄到哪里的  -放信箱吧\N{\rYUANWEN}·Where is it goin- - In the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.25,0:28:43.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是 先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.71,0:28:50.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,信箱
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.72,0:28:56.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,老爷走了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}His Lordship has left?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.30,0:28:57.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 夫人\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, Your Ladyship.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.81,0:28:59.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他早上有会\N{\rYUANWEN}An early appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.65,0:29:10.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但这是穆克罗夫特医生交代的 殿下\N{\rYUANWEN}But it was Dr. Moorcroft's orders, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.94,0:29:13.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我没有怪你 道斯\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm not blaming you, Dawes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.53,0:29:16.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,下次医生来了 我会亲自跟他说\N{\rYUANWEN}I will speak to the doctor myself on his next visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.70,0:29:19.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但在此之前 不要增加剂量了\N{\rYUANWEN}But until then, I do not want the dose increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.91,0:29:22.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我可怜的儿子已经睡得够多了\N{\rYUANWEN}The poor boy sleeps enough as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.75,0:29:24.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 陛下\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.17,0:29:26.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 去照顾他吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you. Please return to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.58,0:29:29.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有问题吗 亲爱的\N{\rYUANWEN}Problem, my dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.71,0:29:31.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有问题也你不需要担心\N{\rYUANWEN}Not one you need concern yourself with...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.84,0:29:34.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,再说你也不愿去担心\N{\rYUANWEN}or would wish to, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.40,0:29:57.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你在干什么 亲爱的  -哦 母亲\N{\rYUANWEN}- What are you doing, dear? - Oh! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.82,0:29:58.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你非要这样吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Must you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.95,0:30:00.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,怎样\N{\rYUANWEN}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.54,0:30:04.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-鬼鬼祟祟的  -我没有鬼鬼祟祟\N{\rYUANWEN}Creep. - Oh, I wasn't creeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.41,0:30:05.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我以为你是内尔\N{\rYUANWEN}I...I thought you were Nell.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.87,0:30:07.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她去商店了 亲\N{\rYUANWEN}She's at the shop, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.92,0:30:10.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rYUANWEN}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.92,0:30:15.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我手帕丢了 我以为\N{\rYUANWEN}I've mislaid a handkerchief, and I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.34,0:30:18.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她洗衣服时 把我的和她的\N{\rYUANWEN}she might have mixed it up with one of hers...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.43,0:30:19.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,弄混了\N{\rYUANWEN}in the wash.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.97,0:30:24.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你该不会觉得\N{\rYUANWEN}You don't think she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.10,0:30:25.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她在偷东西吧\N{\rYUANWEN}stealing from us, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.60,0:30:27.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那也太可怕了\N{\rYUANWEN}I mean, that would be too dreadful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.77,0:30:29.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你说什么啊\N{\rYUANWEN}I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.61,0:30:33.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但仔细想 我们对她确实知之甚少\N{\rYUANWEN}I suppose wewe do know so little about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.94,0:30:36.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不是在暗示什么\N{\rYUANWEN}I wasn't implying that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.03,0:30:42.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,天哪 你也太阴暗太多疑了\N{\rYUANWEN}Good heavens, what a dark and suspicious mind you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.87,0:30:50.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好了出来吧 妈妈 我们不该来这里\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, come out, Mother. We shouldn't be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.63,0:30:54.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rYUANWEN}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.89,0:31:09.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-特伦查德大人  -怎么了\N{\rYUANWEN}Lord Trenchard? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.98,0:31:10.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,夫人在等你\N{\rYUANWEN}Madame is expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.94,0:31:17.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在摸着石头过了一阵子河后\N{\rYUANWEN}There's been some trial and error,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.28,0:31:20.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们已经取得了收支平衡\N{\rYUANWEN}but we now seem to have the balance exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.45,0:31:21.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我希望下周能与\N{\rYUANWEN}I fully expect to be signing a deal
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.70,0:31:23.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大东方公司敲定协议\N{\rYUANWEN}with Great Eastern next week
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.24,0:31:24.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,为他们扩建工程提供轨道\N{\rYUANWEN}to provide the rails for their latest expansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.08,0:31:28.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真是好消息 弗雷德里克\N{\rYUANWEN}This is excellent, Frederick.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.29,0:31:30.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们打算从薄板生产转为毛坯生产\N{\rYUANWEN}We mean to switch to producing"blooms"rather than sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.83,0:31:32.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因为毛坯刚更适合制造铁轨\N{\rYUANWEN}They're better suited to the manufacture of rails.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.00,0:31:37.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这房子一切都没个条理\N{\rYUANWEN}This house. I live in chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.92,0:31:40.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但不会太久了\N{\rYUANWEN}But not for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.22,0:31:43.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是我们修改后的计划\N{\rYUANWEN}I've prepared our revised projections.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.26,0:31:45.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果这笔生意能谈成 我希望谈成\N{\rYUANWEN}If I secure the deal, as I intend to,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.89,0:31:48.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,明年下半年我们就会盈利\N{\rYUANWEN}we should be profitable in the second half of next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.85,0:31:52.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这比预期提前了6个月\N{\rYUANWEN}Six months earlier than anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.94,0:31:54.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我跑了己千英里过来 不想再等了\N{\rYUANWEN}I've traveled 2, 000 miles, and I will not be put off!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.90,0:31:58.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请您稍等 先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Please wait, monsieur!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.28,0:32:00.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我被你深深折服了 弗雷德里克\N{\rYUANWEN}I am greatly impressed, Frederick.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.86,0:32:03.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我必须承认 我们的成功超出了我的预期\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, I must say our success has surpassed my expectations
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.62,0:32:04.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也吊起了我继续\N{\rYUANWEN}and has given me an appetite
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.99,0:32:07.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,合作类似规模\N{\rYUANWEN}to look for schemes on a similar scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.70,0:32:09.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,甚至更大项目的胃口\N{\rYUANWEN}or larger, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.71,0:32:12.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然 您是一个真正的企业家\N{\rYUANWEN}Of course. You are a true entrepreneur.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.25,0:32:15.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,您的胃口永远不会被满足\N{\rYUANWEN}I doubt you will ever be satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.04,0:32:18.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我对投资机会永远持开放态度\N{\rYUANWEN}I would always be open to investment opportunities here...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.26,0:32:19.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,无论是国内还是国外\N{\rYUANWEN}or abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.30,0:32:21.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好的 没问题\N{\rYUANWEN}Good. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.88,0:32:24.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\rYUANWEN}· Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.05,0:32:25.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别 布里克斯先生 请稍等\N{\rYUANWEN}Non, Monsieur Bricus. Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.51,0:32:27.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,天啊 真的很抱歉\N{\rYUANWEN}Mon dieu. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.06,0:32:29.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我帮您问一下她 拜托别往前走了\N{\rYUANWEN}I will ask if she will see you. Stop at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.35,0:32:30.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别碰我\N{\rYUANWEN}Get your hands off of mel
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.98,0:32:33.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,布里卡斯先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Bricus?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.77,0:32:35.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的钱就低人一等吗\N{\rYUANWEN}What is wrong with my money, huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.90,0:32:38.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请你冷静一下好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}May I suggest you calm down?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.15,0:32:41.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你先来找我的 你带着银矿项目先来找的我\N{\rYUANWEN}You came to me. You came to me first with the silver mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.15,0:32:44.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可我现在只能眼睁睁看着朋友赚得盆满钵满\N{\rYUANWEN}and now I am watching my friends make money hand over fist- -
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.12,0:32:45.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那些我推荐给你的朋友\N{\rYUANWEN}friends I sent to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.70,0:32:48.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别嚷嚷了 布里卡斯先生\N{\rYUANWEN}You need to stop shouting, Mr. Bricus.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.54,0:32:49.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的钱就低人一等吗\N{\rYUANWEN}What's wrong with my money?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.91,0:32:52.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只想小心行事 仅此而已\N{\rYUANWEN}I am careful. That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.46,0:32:55.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要对所有的投资人负责\N{\rYUANWEN}I have a responsibility to all my investors.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.38,0:32:57.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而您这样 哭天抢地大喊大叫\N{\rYUANWEN}In the meantime, begging and shouting
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.80,0:32:59.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也绝不会达到你的目的\N{\rYUANWEN}will not advance your cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.34,0:33:00.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\rYUANWEN}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.05,0:33:10.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,太不好意思了 真的 让您看到这尴尬一幕\N{\rYUANWEN}I am mortified. Really, I am so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.14,0:33:12.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我能帮忙吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.19,0:33:15.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不用 谢谢你\N{\rYUANWEN}No. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.27,0:33:17.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,福尔德太太会送您出去的\N{\rYUANWEN}Madame Fourcade will show you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.09,0:33:48.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你好啊  -抱歉 我很忙\N{\rYUANWEN}·Hello. - I'm afraid I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.06,0:33:52.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你今天过得怎么样\N{\rYUANWEN}How was your day?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.98,0:33:56.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我今天一句话就能概括\N{\rYUANWEN}It won't take long to tell you about mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.10,0:33:59.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,独自度过 无事可做\N{\rYUANWEN}I spent it alone, with nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.07,0:34:00.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不好意思 这事很紧急 所以\N{\rYUANWEN}Forgive me, this is urgent, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.98,0:34:04.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比我们的婚姻还急吗\N{\rYUANWEN}More urgent than our marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.40,0:34:06.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\rYUANWEN}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.54,0:34:16.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你找我什么事\N{\rYUANWEN}Did you need me for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.04,0:34:17.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想跟你定个日子\N{\rYUANWEN}I was hoping we might settle on a day
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.67,0:34:20.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,邀请罗切斯特一家过来共进晚餐\N{\rYUANWEN}to ask the Rochesters to dine with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.21,0:34:21.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,明天不是要跟他们吃午饭吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Are we not lunching with them tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.96,0:34:23.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.42,0:34:26.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我想回报他们的美意\N{\rYUANWEN}But I would like to be able to reciprocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.13,0:34:29.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们最近总是盛情款待我们\N{\rYUANWEN}We've enjoyed a great deal of their hospitality of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.60,0:34:31.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们还能邀请侯爵夫人\N{\rYUANWEN}We could invite the Marquise as- -
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.01,0:34:34.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不知道 日子你自己看着定吧\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't know. You may settle on a date if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.02,0:34:35.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我怎么能定呢\N{\rYUANWEN}How can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.23,0:34:37.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们这个状态\N{\rYUANWEN}How can I invite people here...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.65,0:34:41.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我怎么好邀请别人过来 或是出游 或是做些其他事呢\N{\rYUANWEN}or go anywhere or do anything when we are like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.27,0:34:45.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这事我一人解决不了 你得帮帮我\N{\rYUANWEN}I can't solve this on my own. You have to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.19,0:34:46.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我没要求你做什么\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm not asking you to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.57,0:34:49.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我告诉你我的感受了 我们需要时间\N{\rYUANWEN}I've told you what I feel, that we need time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.57,0:34:51.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,除此之外 我对你别无所求\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm asking nothing else of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.03,0:34:53.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我想让你对我有所求\N{\rYUANWEN}But I want you to ask things of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.45,0:34:56.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我需要你这么做\N{\rYUANWEN}I need you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.16,0:34:58.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,克拉拉 我\N{\rYUANWEN}Clara, I
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.21,0:34:59.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\rYUANWEN}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.21,0:35:03.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我今天过得很艰难\N{\rYUANWEN}It has been a difficult day.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.80,0:35:05.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我需要处理一些事\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm trying to deal with something- -
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.88,0:35:07.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一些你不愿告诉我的事\N{\rYUANWEN}Which you do not wish to share with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.05,0:35:08.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我说过我会努力忘记的\N{\rYUANWEN}I have said I will endeavor to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.63,0:35:11.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可你把我拒之门外\N{\rYUANWEN}But you will shut me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.30,0:35:15.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你考虑过我的感受吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Have you once thought of my feelings in all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.81,0:35:17.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,考虑过我的痛苦吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Of what I am suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.27,0:35:18.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.52,0:35:24.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许 你无法接受\N{\rYUANWEN}Perhaps...you will not accept love
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.40,0:35:28.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别人向你伸出援手 主动向你表达爱意\N{\rYUANWEN}from those who offer it, who reach for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.70,0:35:30.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是因为你选择不去接受\N{\rYUANWEN}because you choose not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.58,0:35:35.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是有些自私在身上的\N{\rYUANWEN}There's a selfishness in you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.20,0:35:37.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我之前没意识到\N{\rYUANWEN}which I didn't know was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.81,0:36:06.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是我吗 我的鼻子 给我个鼻子好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is that me? Where's my nose? May I have a nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.70,0:36:11.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你的拉丁语怎么样  -挺好的\N{\rYUANWEN}·And how's your Latin? - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.12,0:36:24.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哦 殿下\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, Your Grace...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.29,0:36:25.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他醒着吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is he awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.88,0:36:28.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,醒着的 陛下\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.89,0:36:36.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.97,0:36:40.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看看你\N{\rYUANWEN}Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.14,0:36:42.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对不起 我好久没来看你了\N{\rYUANWEN}Sorry I haven't been in to see you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.23,0:36:44.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这父亲不太称职\N{\rYUANWEN}Fathers...eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.28,0:36:51.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你喜欢读这个 对吗\N{\rYUANWEN}This is what you enjoy reading, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.78,0:36:56.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,马默杜克《淘气小猫的故事》\N{\rYUANWEN}Marmaduke, The Tale of a Mischievous Kitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.74,0:36:58.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,淘气\N{\rYUANWEN}"Mischievous"?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.62,0:37:00.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,用来形容我挺合适\N{\rYUANWEN}Could be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.41,0:37:04.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大家总是说我很淘气\N{\rYUANWEN}People tell me I'm mischievous all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.33,0:37:08.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我更像是一只又大又邋遢的狗\N{\rYUANWEN}Though I think I'm more of a big, sloppy dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.38,0:37:12.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.05,0:37:13.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们一起读好不好\N{\rYUANWEN}Shall we read it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.69,0:37:30.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,马默杜克 那只淘气的小猫\N{\rYUANWEN}"Marmaduke, the mischievous kitten,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.57,0:37:32.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,蜷曲着躺在篮子里\N{\rYUANWEN}lay curled in a basket
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.40,0:37:37.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-跟他的  -兄弟姐妹在一起\N{\rYUANWEN}with his..."- "Brothers and sisters. "
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.28,0:37:41.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所有的猫都是白底黑点\N{\rYUANWEN}"The kittens were white with black patches,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.37,0:37:44.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,除了马默杜克 他是\N{\rYUANWEN}all except Marmaduke, who was..."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.17,0:37:46.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,橘色的\N{\rYUANWEN}"Orange. "
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.58,0:37:48.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,橘色\N{\rYUANWEN}Orange?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.63,0:37:52.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我好像从没见过橘色的猫 你见过吗\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't think I've ever seen an orange cat before. Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.01,0:38:02.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所有的小猫都睡着了\N{\rYUANWEN}"AII of the kittens were asleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.39,0:38:04.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,爱打呼噜猫在打着呼噜\N{\rYUANWEN}snoring little kitten snores.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.64,0:38:07.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,爱做梦的小猫在做梦\N{\rYUANWEN}Dreaming little kitten dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.40,0:38:08.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,突然间\N{\rYUANWEN}And suddenly there was a..."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.90,0:38:10.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,砰的一声\N{\rYUANWEN}"Thump. "
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.48,0:38:11.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,从走廊那头传来\N{\rYUANWEN}"...from down the hall..."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.79,0:38:23.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-他接下来能睡着吗  -当然\N{\rYUANWEN}Will he sleep now? - Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.45,0:38:26.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,莫克罗夫特开了一堆催眠药\N{\rYUANWEN}Moorcroft and his bromide'll see to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.04,0:38:30.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他睡着的时间比醒着时还要多\N{\rYUANWEN}He spends more time asleep than he does awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.46,0:38:33.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他不该过这样的生活\N{\rYUANWEN}This is no life for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.38,0:38:35.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他应该有更丰富的人生\N{\rYUANWEN}He's so much more than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.72,0:38:38.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们漂亮的儿子\N{\rYUANWEN}Our beautiful boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.41,0:39:00.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,夫人\N{\rYUANWEN}Your Ladyship?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.07,0:39:02.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,您确定要去吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Are you quite certain of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.37,0:39:08.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很抱歉 但去公共画廊是一回事\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm sorry, but a public gallery is one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.50,0:39:11.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可这里是男人的私人住宅\N{\rYUANWEN}but this is a gentleman's private residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.79,0:39:16.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但这里是个工作室 一个画室\N{\rYUANWEN}But it is also a studio. An atelier.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.84,0:39:18.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我也不是一个人 还有你陪着我\N{\rYUANWEN}And I'm not alone. You're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.19,0:39:38.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,夫人\N{\rYUANWEN}Your Ladyship.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.49,0:39:40.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,天啊 真是意外之喜\N{\rYUANWEN}Good heavens. What an exquisite surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.41,0:39:44.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这位是米内特\N{\rYUANWEN}This is Minette.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.37,0:39:47.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请进 请进\N{\rYUANWEN}Come in. Come in, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.04,0:39:51.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好姑娘 真是个好姑娘\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, good girl, good girl. Such a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.63,0:39:57.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,米内特是安妮的女儿\N{\rYUANWEN}- Minette is Annie's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.88,0:40:02.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你见过安妮了吗 应该没有\N{\rYUANWEN}Did you meet Annie? Perhaps not.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.35,0:40:04.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你只在画里见过她\N{\rYUANWEN}You saw her in the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.35,0:40:08.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你来得正好 理查德就在工作室\N{\rYUANWEN}Your timing couldn't be better. Richard's just in his studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.10,0:40:09.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我正希望能看看\N{\rYUANWEN}That's what I was hoping to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.60,0:40:12.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然可以 迪尔登 来客人了\N{\rYUANWEN}Of course. Uh, Dearden? Visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.69,0:40:15.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那 我们帮您拿外套\N{\rYUANWEN}Please, um, allow me to take your coats.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.87,0:40:25.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rYUANWEN}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.92,0:40:34.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,欢迎 夫人\N{\rYUANWEN}Welcome, Your Ladyship.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.63,0:40:36.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 迪尔登先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you, Mr. Dearden.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.13,0:40:37.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,叫我理查德就行\N{\rYUANWEN}Richard, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.55,0:40:39.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,能有这个机会参观我感激不尽\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm grateful for this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.63,0:40:42.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是安妮·哈珀小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}This is Miss Annie Harper.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.93,0:40:45.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-您好  -您好\N{\rYUANWEN}How do you do? - How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.39,0:40:46.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我好像刚见过你女儿了\N{\rYUANWEN}I think I just met your little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.56,0:40:48.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她真漂亮\N{\rYUANWEN}She's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.02,0:40:51.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.02,0:40:52.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这个地方真是安难以置信\N{\rYUANWEN}I can hardly believe this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.77,0:40:54.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会喜欢的\N{\rYUANWEN}I thought you'd like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.15,0:40:59.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,像是炼金术室一样\N{\rYUANWEN}It's like a kind of alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.44,0:41:01.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,确实是\N{\rYUANWEN}It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.49,0:41:06.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你介意吗  -完全不介意\N{\rYUANWEN}·Do you mind? - Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.04,0:41:13.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,狄多 迦太基女王\N{\rYUANWEN}Dido, Queen of Carthage.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.17,0:41:15.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,摄人心魄\N{\rYUANWEN}It's enchanting.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.63,0:41:17.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这离我画完还远着呢\N{\rYUANWEN}It's far from finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.63,0:41:19.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他这人完全不会接受夸奖\N{\rYUANWEN}He doesn't know how to take a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.59,0:41:24.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-还有这一幅  -画了好几个月了\N{\rYUANWEN}And this...Months of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.47,0:41:27.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我还在找寻我的珀蒂塔\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm still searching for my Perdita,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.26,0:41:29.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,说起来真是讽刺\N{\rYUANWEN}which is a little ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.06,0:41:33.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不知道您愿不愿意赏光 夫人\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't suppose you'd oblige, m'lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.48,0:41:37.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\rYUANWEN}Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.32,0:41:41.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只不过在画廊见您第一眼 我就有此意\N{\rYUANWEN}Only I thought it in the gallery as soon as I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.07,0:41:45.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 但还是不了\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you. I think not.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.45,0:41:47.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看来我得继续找了\N{\rYUANWEN}The search continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.24,0:41:52.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,您想来几笔吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Would you like to?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.54,0:41:53.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不敢\N{\rYUANWEN}I daren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.66,0:41:56.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没关系 我可以覆盖掉的\N{\rYUANWEN}I can always paint over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.42,0:41:58.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,稍稍画几笔 来吧\N{\rYUANWEN}The slightest touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.56,0:42:15.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你现在是个艺术家了\N{\rYUANWEN}Now you're an artist. -
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.94,0:42:18.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们打算吃点东西\N{\rYUANWEN}We're gonna have something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.65,0:42:20.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有几个朋友要过来\N{\rYUANWEN}Some friends are joining us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.82,0:42:21.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,欢迎你留下加入\N{\rYUANWEN}I hope you'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.98,0:42:23.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你应该留下\N{\rYUANWEN}You should.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.49,0:42:25.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,其中两位刚从巴黎回来\N{\rYUANWEN}Two of them are just back from Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.24,0:42:27.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可以听他们讲讲故事\N{\rYUANWEN}There'll be tales to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.24,0:42:29.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,您一会儿还有约在身 夫人\N{\rYUANWEN}You have your engagement, Your Ladyship.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.79,0:42:41.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.30,0:42:44.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们等会几就要去罗切斯特家赴约了\N{\rYUANWEN}We shall be leaving for the Rochesters' soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.26,0:42:45.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就不需要备马车了\N{\rYUANWEN}We shan't have need of the carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.68,0:42:47.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很好 老爷\N{\rYUANWEN}Very good, Your Lordship.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.09,0:42:52.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但夫人好像出门了 大人\N{\rYUANWEN}I believe Her Ladyship is out, Your Lordship.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.64,0:42:55.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我敢说 她会及时赶回来的\N{\rYUANWEN}I daresay she intends to return in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.60,0:42:57.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是 她之前说有事要办\N{\rYUANWEN}Uh, yes. I believe she did mention something.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.77,0:43:01.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -老爷\N{\rYUANWEN}·Thank you. - Your Lordship.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.30,0:43:27.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,恐怕克拉拉前面的事\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm afraid Clara has been detained
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.72,0:43:28.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还没办完\N{\rYUANWEN}at a previous appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.97,0:43:31.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对 她的女仆刚传过话了\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, her maid just brought word.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.30,0:43:33.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我真的很抱歉 公爵夫人\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm...really very sorry, Duchess.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.97,0:43:37.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别担心 你一个人来我们也开心\N{\rYUANWEN}Please don't worry. We shall be perfectly satisfied with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.69,0:43:44.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,客人来了\N{\rYUANWEN}We have guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.82,0:43:46.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-终于来了  -奥利弗\N{\rYUANWEN}·Finally. - Olive!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.78,0:43:47.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,从法国乘船而的\N{\rYUANWEN}Off the boat from France.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.99,0:43:51.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你好  -奥利弗\N{\rYUANWEN}How do you do? - Olive.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.45,0:43:52.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你好吗 奥利弗\N{\rYUANWEN}How are you, Olive?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.58,0:43:54.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,特伦查德夫人 这位是西奥\N{\rYUANWEN}Lady Trenchard, this is Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.41,0:43:56.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-很高兴认识你   -西奥很高兴见到你\N{\rYUANWEN}Pleasure to meet you. - Theo, pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.75,0:43:58.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-阿奇博尔德  -你好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Archibald. - How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.92,0:44:01.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,天 我担心记不住你们所有人的名字\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, I'm afraid I shan't remember all these names.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.54,0:44:03.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别担心 夫人\N{\rYUANWEN}Please don't worry about that, Your Ladyship.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.21,0:44:05.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他有时候连自己的名字都不记得\N{\rYUANWEN}He can't remember his name half the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.97,0:44:18.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,跟我们讲讲法国和巴黎的事儿吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Tell us about France. Tell us about Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.60,0:44:20.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,说说那场革命吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Tell us about the revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.40,0:44:21.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哦 那是一个美丽的新世界\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, it's a beautiful new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.77,0:44:24.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们拿起火枪 设立了路障\N{\rYUANWEN}We've got muskets and barricades.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.20,0:45:20.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当我们唱起歌时\N{\rYUANWEN}Quand nous chanterons
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.97,0:45:40.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,邓恩夫人 哈利路亚\N{\rYUANWEN}Mrs. Dunn. Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.10,0:45:44.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我为您准备了君主 院长和主教的座位\N{\rYUANWEN}I shall put you in the seat for monarchs, deans, and bishops.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.52,0:45:46.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,首先 感谢我主\N{\rYUANWEN}First, I thank my God
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.90,0:45:49.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,藉著耶稣基督为你们众人\N{\rYUANWEN}through Jesus Christ for you all,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.69,0:45:53.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,将你的信仰传遍世界\N{\rYUANWEN}that your faith is spoken of throughout the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.40,0:45:55.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,神是我的见证人\N{\rYUANWEN}For God is my witness,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.11,0:45:58.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我为他儿子的福音 用心灵事奉他\N{\rYUANWEN}whom I serve with my spirit in the gospel of His son...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.58,0:46:00.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在我祷告时\N{\rYUANWEN}that without ceasing,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.91,0:46:04.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,常常提及你们的名字\N{\rYUANWEN}I make a mention of you always in my prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.08,0:46:09.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我又求你 若照神的旨意\N{\rYUANWEN}Making request, if by any means now at length,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.13,0:46:11.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如今终能得通达的路\N{\rYUANWEN}I might have a prosperous journey
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.76,0:46:14.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,往你们那里去\N{\rYUANWEN}by the will of God, to come unto you...
